Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》 第二季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里是世界上最广袤的蛮荒之地 远洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它覆盖了地球一半以上的面积{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里全无藏身之处 食物也寥寥无几{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}好比一片海洋沙漠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}长吻原海豚则负责巡视这片沙漠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成群的长吻原海豚聚集在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数量多达五千只{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们利用这一优势 大大增加了捕食的成功几率{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:02:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和住在这里的其他生物一样 它们也要竭尽全力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}才能在这深蓝海洋里安家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}深蓝海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这空旷寂寥的海域里极少会出现生物数量暴涨的情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哥斯达黎加的太平洋海岸附近的灯笼鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}比米诺鱼大不了多少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们体积虽小 但其庞大的数量却弥补了这点不足{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在任何地方 它们都是数量最为庞大的鱼群之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}通常它们只会在夜间才游到水面上觅食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻找浮游生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是现在这一庞大的鱼群却在白天游到了水面上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们几乎可以确定它们是为了产卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}对海豚而言 这可是一大幸事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们用自己的回声定位叫声 锁定了鱼群的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是它们得加快行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为捕猎的动物不止是它们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}黄鳍金枪鱼也发现了灯笼鱼鱼群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们身后 是翼展长达两米的蝠鲼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在轮到了旗鱼 速度在海洋里名列前茅的鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们也加入了捕食的行列当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}灯笼鱼随时都可能回到深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是现在海豚们已经到达这里了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海豚们游到了灯笼鱼鱼群底下 把它们逼到海面上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}迫使它们紧密地聚在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一刻 海浪如沸腾般剧烈翻滚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}金枪鱼以每小时60多公里的速度朝鱼群发起攻击{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}速度不及金枪鱼的蝠鲼最后到达{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们张着巨口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}吞下了数以百计的灯笼鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}灯笼鱼鱼群现在四散而去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}旗鱼瞄准了残留下来的灯笼鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}短短15分钟后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海洋里只剩下一堆银色的鱼鳞碎片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在这里 这种盛宴实在是太过罕见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海豚们在展现了不起的耐力时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他生物却要面临更为严峻的情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们得在这片海洋沙漠里找到食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是一头沉睡的庞然大物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一家子抹香鲸正趁着捕食的间隙好好休息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}谁知道这地球上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最大的脑袋里此刻在做些什么梦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一头有个抹香鲸宝宝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它只有两周大左右 现在它还要靠母乳来填饱肚子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝肚子饿了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它用一阵阵卡嗒声来和母亲沟通{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它的母亲却在沉睡当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝身上覆有䲟鱼 它自己没法赶走䲟鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只能耐着性子忍受着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸酣眠过后精神饱满 准备出发{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸不会等猎物游到海面上来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们要游到深海里去寻找猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了让氧气混入血液当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们连续大口呼吸了几次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着便潜入海底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一家子要一起下潜去找鱿鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸母亲要把自己逼到耐力的极限{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝现在要跟上母亲已经很吃力了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它尽可能地跟上母亲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不时地触碰母亲的身体 好像是为了得到安慰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在水下300米的深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝好像已经没法屏住呼吸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸小时候 往往不参与捕食行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成年抹香鲸继续下潜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸母亲的叫声变大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}变成了节奏更快的卡嗒声{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它现在在用声呐来猎捕鱿鱼群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水深800米处爆发了一阵卡嗒声{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}随后是一片静谧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它已经逮到了猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些抹香鲸在深海底下的时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可能会长达一个小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸母亲终于从深海里回来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的肚子里装满了鱿鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在长久的等待后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}饥饿的抹香鲸宝宝总算可以吃母乳了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸是哺乳动物当中产乳量最多的之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝每天能喝掉一浴缸的母乳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸宝宝要长到六岁才能掌握深海潜游的技术{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那时它才能够自己觅食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正因为深蓝海洋里空荡荡的 捕食动物在这里的生活才会如此艰难{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过也正因为这空旷的环境 所以猎物们在这里才相对安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只海龟宝宝几天前才刚孵出 它现在要离开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}拥挤危险的海岸水域 前往远洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们也是在最近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}才解开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海龟宝宝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}早年的踪迹之谜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}刚开始时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们是靠浮游生物填饱自己的小肚子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们就需要更大的食物来填饱肚子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在每个海洋 离岸数百英里处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都有成群的漂流者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}任何漂浮物都会吸引它们的注意力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一根木头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这根木头可能在海里漂浮了好几年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今它已经成了这个小群落的中心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小河豚也是出于同样的原因来到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这根浮木正是小海龟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一直在寻找的庇护所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这上面不仅有填饱肚子的海草 上面还附着藤壶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过遮掩行踪这点非常重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一头远洋游行的银色小丝鲨也在这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它正在学习辨别什么是美味的食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}什么不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们现在知道了很多小海龟在成年之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会在这类地方待上好几年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哪怕是要面临巨浪席卷 它们也在所不惜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}阳光照在蓝色的深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海面上的水变暖后 便蒸发了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水蒸气上升后凝结成了云{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}云朵不断变大 迅速形成了巨型塔状物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最终生成了大风暴 有的席卷范围还达到了一千六百公里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}飓风迫使气流横扫整片远洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}席卷的海浪甚至高达30米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这里 有些船只沉海后便再无踪迹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年 海上运送的集装箱数量多达一亿三千万个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}平均每天就有四个集装箱会沉入海底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}1992年 几个装着沐浴玩具的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}集装箱在托运途中丢失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}里头装有七千个这样的塑料鸭子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们从阿拉斯加开始了长达一千六百公里的旅行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些鸭子甚至穿过太平洋 来到了澳大利亚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有一些则一路向北漂流{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最终落在了俄罗斯和阿拉斯加之间的海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些鸭子甚至来到了北极地区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一只鸭子在海上漂流了15年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一共穿过了三个大洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最终落到了苏格兰的西海岸上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些鸭子的行踪生动地说明了水流网是如何{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}将所有的海洋连接在一起 形成一个巨大的环流系统{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}深蓝海洋中的很多栖居动物都要依靠这些水流{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}把它们运送至觅食区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大青鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}靠着自己那宽阔的翼形鳍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年要在水流中游行八千多公里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这条鲨鱼可能两个月没进食了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过水流把数英里外的肥厚脂油带到了这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲨鱼可沿途找到自己的下一顿食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}经过数天的游行后 食物的气味越来越浓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一头鲸鱼前不久被船只撞到而丧生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这头鲸鱼或许是一顿丰盛的大餐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过大青鲨得小心些才是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大白鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.57,0:24:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}体重比大青鲨重十倍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而且一心想要独占鲸鱼尸体{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.53,0:25:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大白鲨急切地想要食用富合能量的鲸脂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.57,0:25:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们现在知道鲸脂是大白鲨饮食中的一大构成部分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大白鲨吃饱后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.73,0:25:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大青鲨这类小型鲨鱼就开始收拾残羹冷炙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.49,0:25:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲸鱼尸体的脂油扩散得越广{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.97,0:25:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}越来越多的大青鲨也随之出现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.77,0:26:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在几天之内 鲸鱼尸体的鲸脂就会被一扫而光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.37,0:26:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}失去脂油的尸体无法再漂浮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.89,0:26:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}之后便沉入了海底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这头大青鲨将脂肪存入体内后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.13,0:26:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算不再进食 也能再存活两个月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.93,0:27:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}远洋中一半以上的动物都是漂浮在水流中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.49,0:27:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水母在海洋里四处遨游时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.61,0:27:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}触手勾住什么东西 它们就以这个为食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.85,0:27:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水母的身宽 有时候甚至达一两米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.45,0:27:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}运气好的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们会游到富含浮游动物的海域里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.69,0:27:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这时它们的数量就会迅速增加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.81,0:28:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是一种非常有效的策略{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.61,0:28:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水母是地球上极其常见的一种生命形态{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过在这些水母当中 却有一种形似水母{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.49,0:28:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}实则更加复杂 并且凶险的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.01,0:28:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}名叫葡萄牙战舰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.57,0:29:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的囊内布满气体 囊上是纵向的膜状物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.85,0:29:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正是因为如此 它们才能浮在水中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.73,0:29:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}膜状物充当了帆器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.89,0:29:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪来袭时 它们也能在水中稳妥前行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.01,0:29:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}葡萄牙战舰身后拖着长触须 有些甚至长达30米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.81,0:29:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每根触须上都密布着成千上万个刺细胞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.37,0:29:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一根触须就可以杀死一条鱼 少数情况下 甚至可以杀死一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.41,0:30:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在它致命的触须中间还潜伏着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一种军舰鱼 靠一点点噬咬触须来饱腹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.05,0:30:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算这种鱼对触须上的刺具备一些抵抗力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.81,0:30:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们也要极其小心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.53,0:30:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他鱼类  多半没这么幸运{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.61,0:30:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一根触须逮住了这条鱼 并将它卷了上来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它已经全身麻痹了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.13,0:31:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}专用的强壮触须将猎物递给其他负责消化猎物的触须{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.85,0:31:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}再用强效的化学物质将其液化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.09,0:31:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最后剩下的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只是带鳞屑的外壳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.49,0:31:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只贪婪的葡萄牙战舰水母{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.45,0:31:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可能在一天之内就能捕捉100多条小鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}纵观这片深蓝的海洋 似乎大多数地方都是平淡无奇的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.01,0:32:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}风在海面上恣意吹拂 这里不受陆地的阻隔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.73,0:32:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在海面下 却潜藏着辽阔的山脉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.09,0:32:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}深邃的海沟 与世隔绝的火山高峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.53,0:32:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其纷繁复杂的地貌 远非我们人类的肉眼可看到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.25,0:32:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们也是在最近才注意到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.49,0:32:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}深蓝海洋里的栖息动物具体是如何利用这一特征的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.53,0:33:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一头孤独的鲸鲨踏上了特别的行程{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.77,0:33:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的长度和小型飞机不相上下 体重超过了20吨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.73,0:33:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和很多鲨鱼一样 它不产卵 而是以胎生方式产下幼鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.49,0:33:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它那肿胀的肚子里 装着的幼鲨数量多达300头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.57,0:33:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它或许是海里最大的鱼类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.25,0:34:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过白鲨生下幼鲨的位置 至今无人得知{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.17,0:34:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过今天 我们或许离这个谜底更近了一步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.85,0:34:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们已经知道每年的特定时段{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.73,0:34:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大量的白鲨会出现在加拉帕格斯群岛附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.09,0:34:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们聚集在一个小岛周围{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.93,0:34:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这座陡峭的小岛耸立在深不见底的海水里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.33,0:34:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是达尔文岛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.81,0:34:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这里 漩涡水流将深海里的营养物质带到浅水区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.85,0:34:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}富含营养的海水将各地的鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都纷纷吸引到此处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.85,0:35:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成千上万头双髻鲨来到了这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些双髻鲨几乎全是雌鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们似乎也是到这儿来繁殖的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.45,0:35:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲸鲨受到了热烈的欢迎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.21,0:36:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}长达三米的丝鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.45,0:36:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}上下晃动 摩擦它们粗糙的皮肤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.21,0:36:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这么做或许是为了刮去身上可能附着的寄生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.77,0:36:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些鲨鱼可能会危害到新出生的幼崽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.05,0:36:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了躲开它们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.53,0:36:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲸鲨下潜到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.53,0:36:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水下600米左右的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.45,0:37:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在那里 它或许会产下幼鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.53,0:37:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.05,0:37:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}没有浅水区那样的捕食动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.57,0:37:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}此外食物又非常充足{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.41,0:37:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的宝宝能够在这里长大 最终离去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.41,0:37:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}的确 谁也没在这{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.41,0:37:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲜有人光临的深海位置见过幼仔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.57,0:37:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是事实上 每年都有成百上千头鲸鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会如期来到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}由此可知 海里最大的鱼类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.97,0:37:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就是在这附近诞生长大的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.97,0:38:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}全世界的海洋里分布着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.69,0:38:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}近三万座相当大的岛屿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.37,0:38:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一座就是南乔治亚岛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.25,0:38:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里是海洋动物的理想栖居地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.01,0:38:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了繁殖 它们只能登岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.81,0:38:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}漂泊信天翁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.01,0:38:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们能在海上连续待一年的时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.05,0:39:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}展开那{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.09,0:39:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}宽达3.5米的翅膀滑翔 寻找食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.37,0:39:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它是世上现存的最大鸟类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.93,0:39:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}全世界一共有一万六千只漂泊信天翁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.37,0:39:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在南乔治亚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.97,0:39:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和其他六七个小一点的岛屿上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.57,0:39:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些岛屿都分布在南大洋上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.89,0:39:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在是春天 这只鸟要回到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.73,0:39:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}自己一直居住的巢址上去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.89,0:40:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的终身伴侣已经到这儿了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.25,0:40:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在南乔治亚岛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.89,0:40:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}科学家们对鸟类个体的一生都展开了研究{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.45,0:40:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}研究结果表明这些配偶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会在近40岁时竭尽全力为自己的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.73,0:40:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}创造最好的开始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只雏鸟现在已经几周大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.69,0:40:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它身上依旧覆满了暖和的毛皮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.77,0:41:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它需要父母定期反刍鱼类和鱿鱼来喂养自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.89,0:41:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}由于远洋里的食物非常稀少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这对父母搜遍上万平方公里的范围{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.81,0:41:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}或许只能找到一顿食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.77,0:42:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}年老的父母要在南极的冬天挣扎着活下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.41,0:42:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}将自己的孩子养成健康强壮的大鸟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.33,0:42:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大约130天后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.93,0:42:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雏鸟就开始换毛 长出飞羽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.65,0:42:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的蛋产出九个月后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.57,0:43:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只雏鸟总算准备好挥别父母了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.45,0:43:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们这些年养大的雏鸟里{\r}
