Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.81,0:49:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲜有人见到过的“翻滚海浪”{\r}
