Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.65,0:49:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}渔夫们也对我们说过这事{\r}
