Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.92,0:50:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一现象之所以叫“翻滚海浪”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.86,0:50:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是因为金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.96,0:50:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会冲出海面{\r}
