Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.53,0:50:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了拍摄翻滚海浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.69,0:50:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}拍摄团队必须先找到成群的饵鱼{\r}
