Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.41,0:50:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水深大概是200米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.45,0:50:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}由此可以得知{\r}
