Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.93,0:51:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}遥控操作潜水器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.97,0:51:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在远洋里使用这么重的设备{\r}
